{"tid":565943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得《棟篤特工》係抄Zootopia","createTime":"2018-02-19T12:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T04:05:44.000Z","uid":159734,"like":219,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"573ebc12fc4033d177be61a5bc19ffda918eef44","tid":565943,"uid":159734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以下討論會有劇透，未睇套戲嘅人請即離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先，成套戲講黃子華同佘詩曼查案，搵出令人狂性大發嘅藥物，啊佘角色設定同Zootopia 嘅兔仔Judy Cops一樣，都係警察，要查疑犯，而黃子華就係狡猾嘅私家偵探，好似狐狸啊Nick <br />\n<br />\nZootopia 講有一隻藥可以令茹素和平嘅動物獸性大發襲擊人，棟篤特工就講有隻藥可以令人真正做自己，但會醜態盡現，連故事嘅衝突都抄到足<br />\n<br />\n再加上黃子華為Zootopia 配音，做啊Nick, 有理由相信佢真係照抄Zootopia"},{"pid":"cb7638072ff911456f6e91d84cf1b88ae83d4764","tid":565943,"uid":159734,"like":11,"dislike":64,"score":-53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"而真正嘅幕後黑手都係外表無辜冇咩殺傷力嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/210047_1cc2c760e62d095872540eb476ed8fa3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F210047_1cc2c760e62d095872540eb476ed8fa3.png&h=4eb8f4a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羊咩咩副市長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/210106_fd65de60f96dc2e58081911abdbdfa82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F210106_fd65de60f96dc2e58081911abdbdfa82.png&h=be80006f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHappy Girls 女神Angela"},{"pid":"9fe5cad20ad6b2e5232ec19bd92816a59c8308b4","tid":565943,"uid":159734,"like":8,"dislike":19,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"抄都咁都唔叫侵犯版權，仲好意思話自己創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad18f59bf138231e6b142752e88c19c525279fd","tid":565943,"uid":151933,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"樓主小心"},{"pid":"f0522eed4f1e6735bb5d28921d5c42a6c6328077","tid":565943,"uid":159734,"like":61,"dislike":11,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:07:18.000Z","msg":"《棟篤特工》（英文：Agent Mr Chan）是一部香港偵探式動作喜劇電影，由杜琪峯御用副導演張家傑負責執導，並由黃子華及佘詩曼領銜主演。<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黃子華亦有份為劇本提供構思及意見</span>[1]<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n黃子華知唔知自己點解今次唔洗做票房毒藥啊？因為你抄橋咋！d 觀眾buy 個故事其實係Zootopia 架，啊橋王！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bbf2fa672578e05df504c3851959ad281ea647","tid":565943,"uid":159734,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:07:44.000Z","msg":"推到呢套戲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b88a53a66d6eedad9c1272a21730585e098587f","tid":565943,"uid":17008,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"淨係覺得佢地把聲幾似"},{"pid":"6142afb1481dcab5ccbe258ab1afd2ee57fe547a","tid":565943,"uid":135514,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:12:32.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303183df6fd0407fa0f357cf0558e14ccb55be42","tid":565943,"uid":119450,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"一睇就知劇情完全零crearivity"},{"pid":"ec5ce2ed7baeb3beb71b84622bdac7b16b92ea18","tid":565943,"uid":159734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇過呢兩套戲入黎討論吓"},{"pid":"79e1c1e97fa2e96384f11974b5431a401e13661d","tid":565943,"uid":135514,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"ec5ce2ed7baeb3beb71b84622bdac7b16b92ea18","tid":565943,"uid":159734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇過呢兩套戲入黎討論吓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018